8:
They don't seem very threatening,
but I would prefer we avoid any
unnecessary conflict...
15:
You're sorry, huh? Not sorry enough,
brat!
19: Hoppity hop, it's time to STOP!
21:
She's never further than a hop, skip,
and a jump away...
27:
Able to leap across the ocean in a
single bound! Never fear, the Marine
Bunny Princess Faroa is here!
30:
Faroa, our hero! We've been waiting
for you!
40:
Just call my name, and I'll be there!
See you around, everyone!
44:
Was she... a bounty hunter? She's
unlike any other I've met before...
47:
Definitely a popular one around
here, at least...
49:
Ho-ho... Seems like I've got some
new fans.
52:
The bunny Champion with the boy
and girl. You're Alk, Stella, and Light,
right?
61:
Heard about ya from one of my
sponsors! You guys are bounty
hunters too, right?
65:
I have a favor to ask, actually. Could
you help me save the people of this
Float?
71:
Those pirates have been nothing
but trouble since they arrived here.
They're throwing their weight around
and doing whatever they want with
the place.
74:
You seem quite knowledgeable
about this.
78:
My sponsor filled me in. You guys
know Quazer, right?
86:
I also got help from the head of a
shipping business and a Gaean
officer buddy of mine to find out
what's been going on.
96:
Hehe! My networking skills are pretty
decent, not gonna lie!
100:
But there are just a few too many
troublemakers for me to deal with
alone.
103:
And that's where you come in! It'll go
a lot smoother with help...
107:
And I'll give some of the reward to
you guys, too!
112: ...What kind of split are we looking at?
116: Depends on how well you do!
120:
Okay, then. Guess we're working for
it.
126:
All right, that's what I was hoping to
hear! Try to keep up, m'kay?
132:
My, what an audience! I hope you're
all ready for a spectacular
beatdown!
135: Thank you, Faroa! We love you!
139:
Thanks! If you're ever in a bind, I'll
hop right on over!
147:
A hero... 
She reminds me of Marina.
152:
Huh?! You don't mean... THAT Marina,
do you?
161:
You gotta be kidding me! A grand
adventure with the Crimson
Blades?! Sounds amazing!
165:
I think we were all destined to meet
each other!
168:
I'll be a huge help to you guys, you
have my word!
171:
And this bunny of the seas always
keeps her word!
180:
U-um... In the north, where it's cold.
Too cold for even the merfolk from
around here to live!
184:
Shouldn't sea bunnies live
underwater? I haven't seen you
swim before.
189:
M-my mission is to connect the
people on land and sea together!
193:
Okay, I get it now. We welcome you,
Faroa.
196:
She's amazing. A great performer,
too. Do you think she does acting?
201:
Haha... Looks like we might have a
real big shot on board, now.
